gw.api.builder

Class AccountContactBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<AccountContact,AccountContactBuilder>
      • gw.api.builder.AccountContactBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueGenerator<AccountContact>

    public class AccountContactBuilder
extends DataBuilder<AccountContact,AccountContactBuilder>
    Builder class for creating a new AccountContact in PolicyCenter. The AccountBuilder may generate a Contact at bean creation time if the Contact is not explicitly set to null, or a Contact is not supplied. Some simple usage examples: 
       new AccountContactBuilder().withDefaultContact().asAccountHolder().createAndCommit()
   new AccountContactBuilder().withContact(new PersonBuilder()).createAndCommit()
   new AccountContactBuilder().asNamedInsured().asBillingContact().withContact(new CompanyBuilder()).createAndCommit()
